Owlhawk zoomed out of the way, but this caused his
wing to once again surge with pain.  He screamed and
then sent a comm message down to Proto.

Owlhawk:  Congradulations Proto, you are the first to
be infected with the Vok Destroyer.  In a few weeks
you will experience a spasm of momentary pain, then a
few days later it will happen again, then it will
continue as your spark breaks down constantly getting
more and more frequent until it occurs every few
minutes, you won't be able to sleep for the pain, you
won't be able to eat for risk of choking during an
attack.  Then when the spasms join together in a never
ending barrage of pain you will experience the most
painful, and last few hours of you life.  Depending on
how strong you are this may take from 8 months to 2
years.  One last thing, I'm the only one in the
universe who can cure you.
